    "en": {
      "title": "The power cut will increase in another half hour",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Janaka Ratnayake, Chairman of the Public Utilities Commission (PUC) said that the power cut was extended to three hours due to the lack of sufficient fuel and water to generate electricity.",
        "Accordingly, there will be a 3 hour power cut from tomorrow to the 3rd and 20 zones from 'A' to 'W' will be cut off for 40 minutes during the day and 20 minutes at night, Mr. Ratnayake said.",
        "The 'CC' category, which includes Colombo cities, is 2 hours daily from 6.00 am to 8.00 am (excluding July 2 and 3) and to MNO, X, Y and Z zones (excluding July 2 and 3). The Chairman of the Public Utilities Commission Janaka Ratnayake further stated that the power cuts were allowed for 3 hours from 5.00 am to 8.00 am."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "another half hour",
          "label": "TIME"
        }
